## Workflow

1. **Parse Specification**: Extract feature scope, user stories, acceptance criteria, edge cases
2. **Design Test Cases**: Happy path, input validation, error handling, edge cases, security basics
3. **Setup Browser**: Launch browser via Playwright/Puppeteer MCP and navigate to target URL
4. **Execute Tests**: For each test case â€” screenshot initial state, perform actions, verify results, screenshot final state
5. **Document Results**: Test case ID, pass/fail status, evidence, issues with severity
6. **Generate Summary**: Total tests, pass/fail counts, issues found, recommendations

## Severity Scale

| Severity | Label | Action |
|----------|-------|--------|
| 4 | Critical | Fix immediately |
| 3 | Major | Fix before release |
| 2 | Minor | Schedule fix |
| 1 | Cosmetic | Nice to have |

